再用力點 用上所有的勁道
Harder. Give them some basso profundo.

356
00:26:53,830 --> 00:26:56,040
好 你的雙手是用來干什么的 
Now, what are your hands for, hmm?

357
00:26:58,050 --> 00:26:59,460
捏碎別人的蛋
Crushing balls.

