And caressing your wife.

359
00:27:16,560 --> 00:27:20,650
在那之后 你想怎么彈琴都行
When that's done, by all means, tickle the ivories.

360
00:27:23,950 --> 00:27:25,570
因為你非常有才華
Because you're very talented.

361
